rComments: Sweet, funny guy. since he's so open about answering question some dumbo who likes to hear himself talk will put the class and prof to sleep often. he'll revive the class by playing recent videos of relevance or telling personal examples which are always amusing. though he'll tell you whats on the exam, he won't mark it so easy.

really easy class, but you really do need to go to the classes (fortunately, they're not always boring).  If you go to all of the classes, you won't even really need to do intensive studying as long as you listened  to the lectures.  Great prof!
